v1.helmValues:
replicaCount: 2
image:
  repository: nginx
  tag: stable
v1.helmValuesDefaults:
replicaCount: 1
image:
  repository: nginx
  tag: stable

patches./deployment.yaml:
apiVersion: apps/v1beta2
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  labels:
    app: my-app
    chart: values-update
    heritage: Tiller
    release: values-update
  name: deployment
spec:
  template:
    spec:
      $setElementOrder/containers:
      - name: values-update
      containers:
      - imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
        name: values-update

metadata.name: values-update
metadata.releaseNotes: add static chart (will not be updated)
